{"tid":476684,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 手機又爆炸，好似放煙花噴火","createTime":"2017-11-22T08:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T19:08:18.000Z","uid":1130,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"21659864583ca35d1c7e22c20b1b910ae7e8a353","tid":476684,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"Source:<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2017/11/17/samsung-note2-explosion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2Fsamsung-note2-explosion%2F&d=iZ8SjhuwUcEPij6oaX2b4AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1e51fc76\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2017/11/17/samsung-note2-explosion/</a><br />\n<br />\n近幾年以來，手機爆炸的報導總是不斷的浮現在我們的視野裡。就如最近事件吧：山東省壽光市就發生了一起典型案例。監控影片記錄下手機自燃爆炸的完整畫面。那畫面，隔著遠遠的屏幕都能感覺到驚心動魄。監控影片顯示，11月13日早上，山東壽光，一市民在吃早餐時，桌上的手機突然在劇烈抖動就像在跳舞一樣、手機充電、音頻孔不斷地向外冒火花，並且電池從手機裡飛出，手機殼不停地在冒煙，嚇壞了機主。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2017/11/22/5a15344135700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.loli.net%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F5a15344135700.jpg&h=baee0475&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58aa4b17a78168a5be69e19279fe54c91e4a7117","tid":476684,"uid":1130,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多即刻睇GIF<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/9RVVg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2F9RVVg.gif&h=1bf95707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從記者與市民的對話中，可以了解到，手機是 Galaxy Note 2 ，手機電池是原裝的，但已經用了四年了。其實電池用了那麼久，安全本來就沒有得到保障了，一般電池的壽命為3年左右，電池爆炸有以上四種可能，但具體是哪個還沒有調查清楚，不過市民已向 Samsung 客服反映情況。相信不久之後我們就可以知道原因了。"},{"pid":"cebfc441d4f23e19bfac980ebfe49641e0bed4d5","tid":476684,"uid":87506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:36:43.000Z","msg":"好彩佢行開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係會搞出人命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e81621958262fe7beff5b8139f014736ed9f85d","tid":476684,"uid":29273,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"Note 2 ?<br />\nNote 8都出埋啦"},{"pid":"7bbde413ad9a9cc8da11eae778d546611b6b81c8","tid":476684,"uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"samsung正垃圾！"},{"pid":"43564525f3ca6079d143528dfae57d0022120548","tid":476684,"uid":23677,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"舊電緊急彈出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2770e15861e9a7ee9458841905e324461474a3","tid":476684,"uid":33456,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊電緊急彈出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n安全移除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74702fbddd18185eff508105f55bdeb7d9101e90","tid":476684,"uid":128613,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/180827_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F180827_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e0e0bd06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3d25cc6b83c70bac1b7230a25810d17f41c4ec2","tid":476684,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"古惑的電話"},{"pid":"e4f0ef114fc6c7541d173272478198c9779a01da","tid":476684,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"舊電幾安全，識自己閃走，<br />\n高科技智能生命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af1ef56c32af2201a97a2e15bf5973aa6c070db","tid":476684,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22